'Yan Welsh AMs sun damu da 'kamar wawaye'
Wasu AMs suna da damuwa game da shawarar canza sunayensu zuwa MWPs (Mambobin Majalisar Welsh).
Wannan matsalar ta taso ne saboda shirin sauya sunan majalisa zuwa Welsh Parliament.
AMs a duk faɗin fagen siyasa sun nuna damuwa cewa wannan shawarar na iya zama abin dariya.
Wani dan Labour AM ya ce "yana da matsala tare da Twp da Pwp" wanda ya haifar da damuwa a cikin kungiyar.
Ga masu karatu a waje da Wales: Twp na nufin rashin hankali a harshen Welsh, kuma pwp na nufin rashin hankali.
Wani mai buga AM ya ce kungiyar ta "rashin jin daɗi" kuma ta ba da shawarar wasu sunaye.
Wani dan kasar Welsh mai ra'ayin mazan jiya ya ce kungiyarsa na da "hankali mai zurfi" game da sauya sunan, amma ya ce wannan wani nau'i ne na muppets ko wawaye daga MWP.
A wannan yanayin, ana furta haruffan Welsh na w kamar yadda ake furta u a Yorkshire Turanci.
Kwamitin Majalisar da ke shirya dokar canza sunayen yanzu ya ce: "Mambobin za su yanke shawara ta ƙarshe game da cikakkun bayanai game da abin da za a kira membobin majalisar".
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017, ta ba da izinin majalisa ta Welsh ta canza sunanta.
A watan Yuni, hukumar ta fitar da wani rahoto kan shawarwarin da ta bayar, inda ta nuna cewa akwai goyon baya sosai ga kiran majalisar dokokin da Welsh Parliament.
Game da taken AMs, Hukumar ta goyi bayan sunan 'yan majalisar dokokin Welsh ko WMPs, amma sunan MWP ya sami goyon bayan jama'a.
Kamar yadda AMs ke ba da shawarar wasu zaɓuɓɓuka, amma yanke shawara tare da yarjejeniya na iya zama ciwon kai ga mai gudanarwa na yanzu, Elin Jones. Ana sa ran Elin Jones za ta gabatar da kwafin dokar game da canje-canje a cikin 'yan makonni.
Dokar gyare-gyare ta ƙunshi wasu canje-canje a cikin tsarin majalisa, ciki har da dokoki don ƙin AMs da kuma tsarin tsarin kwamitin.
AMs suna da damar yin kuri'ar ƙarshe game da tambayar abin da za a kira su yayin tattauna dokar.
'Yan Macedonia sun yi zabe don su canja sunan ƙasar
Masu jefa kuri'a za su yi zabe a ranar Lahadi don yanke shawara ko za su canza sunan kasar zuwa Jamhuriyar Arewacin Macedonia.
An gudanar da zaben ne domin warware takaddama ta shekaru da dama da ke tsakanin kasar da makwabciyarta Girka, wacce ke da yankinta mai suna Macedonia.
Athens ma ta nace cewa sunan makwabciyarta ta arewa yana wakiltar mallakar yankin ta, kuma ta yi tir da ƙoƙarinta na samun membobin EU da NATO.
Shugaban kasar Macedonia, Gyorgy Ivanov, wanda ke adawa da karbar kuri'ar sauya sunan, ya ce ba zai mutunta kuri'ar ba.
Duk da haka, masu goyon bayan kuri'ar, ciki har da Firayim Minista Zoran Zaev, sun yi jayayya cewa canjin sunan ne farashin da za a biya don shiga EU da NATO.
