The Methodist addini na asali whites tafi a cikin 1930s.
Wani rukunin addinin baki da ke bauta a kusa da wurin ya karɓi ginin.
Wani rukunin masu baƙar fata a ƙarƙashin jagorancin Reverend John Howard Johnson ya mamaye St. Martin's. Reverend John Howard Johnson ya jagoranci gwagwarmaya da 'yan kasuwa a kan 125th Street, babban titi na Harlem, wanda ya ƙi ɗaukar bakaken fata ko kuma ya ƙi ba su ci gaba.
Ginin ya yi matukar lalacewa a lokacin bala'in wuta a 1939. Amma mabiyan Parish na Uba Johnson suna da shirin sake gina ginin, kuma Carillon ya ba da aikin.
Reverend David Johnson, wanda shine ɗansa kuma magajin St. Martin, ya yi alfahari da kiran Carillon "kwana na matalauta".
