Tiffany Ng, masanin ilimin kimiya a Jami'ar Michigan, ta ce wannan shi ne karillon na farko a duniya da dan wasan kwaikwayo na baki, DiNisio A. Lind, ya buga. Lind ya koma coci na Riverside don yin wasa da karillon mai girma shekaru 18 da suka gabata.
