Wani kifi ya ji wa yaro ɗan shekara 13 rauni yayin da yake yin ruwa a California
Jami'ai sun ce wani ɗan shekara 13 da ya yi tsalle zuwa cikin ruwa don kama lobster a ranar fara kakar lobster a California, ya ji rauni bayan wani ɗan kifi ya kai masa hari.
An kai harin ne da karfe 7 na safe a kusa da bakin rairayin bakin teku na Bacon a Encinitas.
Chad Hammell, wanda ya yi magana da KSWB-TV a San Diego, ya ce ya ji wani yaro yana kuka don taimako yayin da yake nutsewa tare da abokai na kusan rabin sa'a a safiyar Asabar, kuma ya tafi jirgin ruwa tare da wasu mutane don fitar da yaron daga cikin ruwa.
