Daniel Sturridge ya tsallake rashin nasarar da Liverpool ta sha da Chelsea a wasan Premier League da aka yi a Stamford Bridge, London, ranar Asabar, ta hanyar zura kwallo a minti na 89.
A lokacin da aka ci 1-0, Sturridge ya karɓi ƙwallo daga Jerdon Shakiri, kusan yad 30 daga ƙwallo na Chelsea.
Ya buga kwallon a hannun hagu kafin ya duba zuwa ga post mai nisa.
