Dole ne Amurka ta ninka kudaden AI
Kai-Fu Lee, wani mai saka jari da kuma masanin AI wanda ya yi aiki ga Google, Microsoft da Apple, ya ce, yayin da China ke kara shiga cikin aikin kere kere, ya kamata Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take kashewa kan bincike a fannin.
Duk da cewa Amurka ba ta da wata dabarar AI ta yau da kullun, waɗannan bayanan suna zuwa ne bayan ɓangarori daban-daban na gwamnatin Amurka sun yi sanarwar AI.
A halin yanzu, China ta gabatar da shirin ta a bara: tana da burin zama No. 1 a cikin kirkirar AI nan da shekarar 2030.
"Yin ninki biyu na kasafin kudin bincike na AI kyakkyawan farawa ne, tunda duk sauran kasashe sun yi nisa fiye da Amurka kuma muna neman ci gaba a AI", in ji Lee.
A cikin wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon, Lee ya ce ninka tallafin zai iya ninka yiwuwar babbar nasarar AI ta gaba a Amurka.
Lee, wanda littafinsa "AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley da New World Order" ya fito a wannan watan ne daga Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, Shugaba na Cinovation Ventures, wanda kuma ya zuba jari a cikin Face ++, daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI na kasar Sin.
A cikin shekarun 1980s a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon, ya yi aiki a kan tsarin AI, wanda ya doke Otello Player na Amurka, kuma daga baya ya kasance mai zartarwa a Microsoft Research kuma shugaban kamfanin Google na kasar Sin.
Lee ya karbi gasar fasahar gwamnatin Amurka ta baya, irin su Robotics Challenge na Hukumar Bincike na Tsaro, kuma ya tambayi lokacin da zai biyo baya don taimakawa wajen gano masu bincike na gaba.
Lee ya ce masu bincike a Amurka suna bukatar yin aiki tuƙuru don samun tallafin gwamnati.
"Ba China ke fitar da shugabannin ilimi ba, kamfanoni ne", in ji Lee.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun dauki malamai daga jami'o'i don yin aiki a kan AI a cikin 'yan shekarun nan.
Lee ya ce canje-canje a cikin manufofin shige da fice na Amurka zai taimaka wajen haɓaka ƙoƙarin AI.
"Ina tsammanin dole ne a ba da katunan kore ta atomatik ga masu PhD a AI", in ji shi.
Majalisar Jiha ta kasar Sin ta fitar da shirin bunkasa AI na gaba a watan Yuli na 2017.
Lee ya ce, "Kyakkyawan aikin ilimi a China ya yi kasa, duk da cewa National Science Foundation da sauran hukumomin gwamnati suna ba da kudade ga mutane a cibiyoyin ilimi kamar yadda suke ba da kudade ga masu binciken Amurka".
A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Haɗin Kai ta Artificial Intelligence, wanda aka nufa don haɗa abokan hulɗa daga masana'antu da ilimi, kuma Fadar White House ta sanar da cewa za ta kafa Kwamitin Zaɓaɓɓen Artificial Intelligence.
Kuma a wannan watan, DARPA ta sanar da saka hannun jari na dala biliyan 2 a wani shiri mai suna AI Next.
NSF a halin yanzu tana saka sama da dala miliyan 100 a shekara a cikin binciken AI.
A halin yanzu, dokar Amurka da ke kokarin kafa hukumar tsaro ta kasa kan kere kere ba ta samu ci gaba ba cikin watanni da dama.
