A karo na biyu a cikin wata daya, Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia a ranar Asabar, inda ya lashe zaben 2016 da kashi 40 cikin 100 na kuri'un da aka kada.
Trump ya nemi taimakon dan takarar Sanata na Jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia Patrick Morris, wanda ya sha kaye a zaben.
Simon Haider, wani masanin kimiyyar siyasa a jami'ar West Virginia, ya ce, "ba kyakkyawan alama ba ne ga Morris cewa Trump zai zo don karfafawa a zaben", in ji Reuters.
